{"tid":1030703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"秘魯酒店遭搶劫數十遊客曾被挾持兩港旅行團41人入住","createTime":"2019-02-21T06:26:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-22T15:50:54.000Z","uid":39521,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f485f7ea452f9c0dfbf9c56681a76cd584eb657d","tid":1030703,"uid":39521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T06:26:40.000Z","msg":"秘魯東部馬德雷德迪奧斯（Madre de Dios）Inkaterra酒店當地時間2月19日晚，遭約10名匪徒持槍搶劫，劫匪搶奪財物，殺害一名秘魯籍導遊後逃去。外媒報道，數十名遊客曾被挾持，而據中國駐秘魯大使館消息，當時酒店有香港旅行團入住，共有41名中國籍遊客，沒有人傷亡，但其中一名遊客護照被搶。<br />\n<br />\n旅遊業議會總幹事陳張樂怡向《明報》證實，41人都是香港人。她表示，酒店當時有兩團旅行團入住，分別是捷旅假期南美四國團（19名團員、1領隊）及尊賞假期南美五國團（20名團員、1領隊），當中秘魯行程是捷旅假期旅行團的第一站。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，捷旅假期旅行團有一名團員被搶護照，一名團員被搶手機。兩團旅行團會繼續行程，而遺失護照團友須留在當地完成補領等程序後才跟上。<br />\n（環球網／世界日報）"},{"pid":"4d399506e5db0b2e3594e3dbb563b1a429e07f42","tid":1030703,"uid":49392,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T06:27:38.000Z","msg":"吳京.jpg"},{"pid":"c48c49281a64991e5e853931ff99e3671d8f2ddf","tid":1030703,"uid":39521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T06:27:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20190221/s00005/1550725130374/%e7%a7%98%e9%ad%af%e9%85%92%e5%ba%97%e9%81%ad%e6%90%b6%e5%8a%ab%e6%95%b8%e5%8d%81%e9%81%8a%e5%ae%a2%e6%9b%be%e8%a2%ab%e6%8c%be%e6%8c%81-%e5%85%a9%e6%b8%af%e6%97%85%e8%a1%8c%e5%9c%9841%e4%ba%ba%e5%85%a5%e4%bd%8f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20190221%2Fs00005%2F1550725130374%2F%25e7%25a7%2598%25e9%25ad%25af%25e9%2585%2592%25e5%25ba%2597%25e9%2581%25ad%25e6%2590%25b6%25e5%258a%25ab%25e6%2595%25b8%25e5%258d%2581%25e9%2581%258a%25e5%25ae%25a2%25e6%259b%25be%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e6%258c%25be%25e6%258c%2581-%25e5%2585%25a9%25e6%25b8%25af%25e6%2597%2585%25e8%25a1%258c%25e5%259c%259841%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e5%2585%25a5%25e4%25bd%258f&d=IyvsStEAH7GPomOhwpmPFQogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=980e2157\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20190221%2Fs00005%2F1550725130374%2F%25e7%25a7%2598%25e9%25ad%25af%25e9%2585%2592%25e5%25ba%2597%25e9%2581%25ad%25e6%2590%25b6%25e5%258a%25ab%25e6%2595%25b8%25e5%258d%2581%25e9%2581%258a%25e5%25ae%25a2%25e6%259b%25be%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e6%258c%25be%25e6%258c%2581-%25e5%2585%25a9%25e6%25b8%25af%25e6%2597%2585%25e8%25a1%258c%25e5%259c%259841%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e5%2585%25a5%25e4%25bd%258f&h=99926413\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20190221/s00005/1550725130374/%e7%a7%98%e9%ad%af%e9%85%92%e5%ba%97%e9%81%ad%e6%90%b6%e5%8a%ab%e6%95%b8%e5%8d%81%e9%81%8a%e5%ae%a2%e6%9b%be%e8%a2%ab%e6%8c%be%e6%8c%81-%e5%85%a9%e6%b8%af%e6%97%85%e8%a1%8c%e5%9c%9841%e4%ba%ba%e5%85%a5%e4%bd%8f</a>"},{"pid":"a10f31217c88923d6e2b3f468a7c281017daf602","tid":1030703,"uid":110832,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T06:51:00.000Z","msg":"收到風 支那秘密部隊 戰狼 已經動身去緊當地<br />\n相信好快會有好消息<br />\n<br />\n「犯我中華者，雖遠必誅！」<br />\n「當你在海外遭遇危險，不要放棄！請記住，在你身後，有一個強大的祖國！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係咁潮濕嘅天氣都可以打冷震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2292dc1afb26306459ed49dbe350032bb0ad9e8","tid":1030703,"uid":61018,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T06:53:19.000Z","msg":"個賊都幾叻<br />\n識搶中國嘅護照<br />\n咁吴京就可以安全帶佢回中國了"},{"pid":"b5b3e116a92d7482f9d7736bad5b1b9ac6c1b43f","tid":1030703,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T06:54:24.000Z","msg":"2047"},{"pid":"ca7b0e9b36aac5da80a06221da48743bc9915330","tid":1030703,"uid":57376,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T06:54:28.000Z","msg":"兩團旅行團會繼續行程，而遺失護照團友須留在當地完成補領等程序後才跟上。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有心情繼續旅遊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cf6eedfb5b82c6a5d4e33696b99916380e8caaf","tid":1030703,"uid":39521,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ca7b0e9b36aac5da80a06221da48743bc9915330","tid":1030703,"uid":57376,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T06:54:28.000Z","msg":"兩團旅行團會繼續行程，而遺失護照團友須留在當地完成補領等程序後才跟上。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有心情繼續旅遊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T07:09:28.000Z","msg":"港豬：我使咗成皮嘢㗎"},{"pid":"23c34ef5eb5b8334ec52379f4ec2fb87db821361","tid":1030703,"uid":38376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T09:47:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190221/59286038\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190221%2F59286038&d=IyvsStEAH7GPomOhwpmPFQogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=65954745\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190221%2F59286038&h=0dabf4aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190221/59286038</a><br />\n<br />\n【港人秘魯遇險】旅議會指41名團友受驚但無傷 1人被搶護照滯留當地<br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n...暫時已知捷旅假期有兩名團友分別被搶去護照及手提電話，被搶護照的團友因而滯留秘魯當地等候補辦證件，其餘團友經商議後決定繼續行程...<br />\n<br />\n...陳太續稱，<span style=\"color: blue;\">期望護照被搶的一名捷旅團友能趕及在巴西與其餘團友會合，否則該團友只有從秘魯直接返港</span>，另尊賞假期全部團友亦已決定繼續行程...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">又係不得不吹奏BNO嘅時候<br />\n呢件事入面，如果你拎廁板護照，你嘅下場就係，補領「中國旅行証」for你直接從秘魯返港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你拎嘅係BNO，當然補領完「英國緊急護照」之後就可以繼續行程啦<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"08504641b0444cfa8730f7e3e454c3e78a642938","tid":1030703,"uid":191572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cf6eedfb5b82c6a5d4e33696b99916380e8caaf","tid":1030703,"uid":39521,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ca7b0e9b36aac5da80a06221da48743bc9915330","tid":1030703,